lead_paragraph: Anthony Wall of England won his first European Tour title in more than 16 years, beating Alex Noren of Sweden 1 up in the final of the Paul Lawrie Match Play on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Wall Beats Noren to Win Paul Lawrie Match Play
